title: Keity's Mom Tells These Listeners If Their Relationship Is Gonna Work Out
description:
Our producer Keity's mom has an uncanny ability - she can read someone and tell you all about them, JUST from a picture. Want her to judge the person you’re dating? Maybe she can save you some time and tell you if the relationship is gonna work out before you even go on a date!
